title: Atlantis series (4 books) by Gena Showalter (Perseu)
description:
Grace Carlyle's world was about to change . . .

Deep in the jungle on the trail of her missing brother, Grace never
expected to find a secret world populated by mythological monsters
nor guarded by a sword-wielding being whose beauty put mortal men
to shame. Darius en Kragin belongs to a race of shape-shifting warriors
sworn to guard Atlantis and kill all travelers who stray within its
boundaries. Yet when Grace stumbles into his realm, he finds himself
tempted to betray his centuries-old vow. Now their forbidden love will
either bring their worlds together -- or tear them both apart.

Atlantis series (4 books)
By: Gena Showalter
